<div class="txtcont">
													
													
													<p> https://www.mafengwo.cn/i/3042687.html </p> 
<p><br></p> 
<p> </p> 
<p> </p> 
<p> </p> 
<p> </p> 
<p> 这篇游记豪迈地提到了：<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/i/3042687.html#">十丈洞</a>，<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/i/3042687.html#">四洞沟</a>，<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/i/3042687.html#">丙安古镇</a>，<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/i/3042687.html#">佛光岩</a>，<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/i/3042687.html#">大同古镇</a></p> 
<p> 四月的<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10208.html">重庆</a>旅行，忽然想到还有一个地儿应该挺顺路：<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>。去<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14103.html">贵州</a>时，去黄果树，曾想去<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>，但路途好远，汽车从<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11239.html">贵阳</a>到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>不堵车至少要6~7小时，于是放弃。这次去<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10208.html">重庆</a>又想到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>，原来从<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10208.html">重庆</a>去<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>只要3~4小时！于是……<br> <br> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html"> 赤水</a>位于川渝黔交界的<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14103.html">贵州</a>省<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10376.html">遵义</a>市，因红军“四渡<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>出奇兵”而名扬天下。<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>不但有美名，还有美景。“<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>丹霞”是青年早期丹霞地貌的代表，面积1200多平方公里，是全国面积最大、发育最美丽壮观的丹霞地貌。&nbsp;<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>丹霞与<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://baike.baidu.com/view/8581.htm">湖南</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;崀山、<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://baike.baidu.com/view/7340.htm">广东</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;丹霞山、<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://baike.baidu.com/view/2812.htm">福建</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/17407.html">泰宁</a>、<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15508.html">江西</a>龙虎山、<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://baike.baidu.com/view/4150.htm">浙江</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;江郎山等6大著名丹霞地貌景区组合成为“<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://baike.baidu.com/view/2692077.htm">中国丹霞</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;”，并在第34届世界遗产大会上通过表决，成为我国第8个<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://baike.baidu.com/view/358421.htm">世界自然遗产</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;项目。<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>还多产“瀑布”，其中著名的“<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>大瀑布”不逊黄果树。<br> <br></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33567841.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file26.mafengwo.net/M00/A8/A5/wKgB4lNjKHiAdOjSABIdQ406DRk13.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a></p> 
<p> &nbsp;<br> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10208.html"> 重庆</a>汽车站（即菜园坝汽车站。位置是挨着火车站的，不是立交桥对面的菜园坝长途汽车站）每天早七点开始有发往<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>的大巴，间隔40分钟一班，票价70。从<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10208.html">重庆</a>到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63054.html">合江</a>是高速，从<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63054.html">合江</a>下高速到九支（九支归属<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12703.html">四川</a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13518.html">泸州</a>，与<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>市一河之隔，但由于九支-<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>大桥年久失修，只允许走小车，所以到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>的大巴只能停靠九支客运站）的路差些，好在客运站就在桥头，有很多<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>的出租车往来（起车费4元，所需之处基本可到达），还是很方便的。<br> <br></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33567842.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file26.mafengwo.net/M00/A8/41/wKgB4lNjKBaAKHnNAAVkhSSwqmk60.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a></p> 
<p> &nbsp;<br> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html"> 赤水</a>的客运站还要提前介绍一下以防混乱：<br> 1、<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>客运站即（老客运站），位于人民西路。有从<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>市到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15973.html">十丈洞</a>瀑布（<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>大瀑布）、<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15975.html">四洞沟</a>瀑布群、杨家岩（红石野谷）、<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15943.html">丙安古镇</a>、<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15942.html">大同古镇</a>的景区公交车。<br> 2、<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>旅游客运站（是新客运站），位于河滨西路。去<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩</a>、五柱峰需要从这里走，没有景区专车，应乘到“太平渡”的车，买到“大群”的票，上车和司乘说明到“<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩</a>”，他们会让你在<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩</a>景区大门下车。<br> <br></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33567843.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/A8/BC/wKgB4lNjKJeALwQgAAN3heW0Ysk91.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a></p> 
<p> <br> D1（2014-04-02）：<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10208.html">重庆</a>-<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>-<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15943.html">丙安古镇</a>，住<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>。<br> 早7点40大巴有<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10208.html">重庆</a>出发，约4小时到达九支，打车到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>客运站，转车<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15943.html">丙安古镇</a>。<br> 到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15943.html">丙安古镇</a>的小面非常破烂（我还从没坐过这样破烂的车，但走过同样烂的路以后我就理解了），坐满即走。<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15943.html">丙安古镇</a>有千年历史，旧时为<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>河航运最繁荣的水陆码头。1935年1月红军四渡<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>时，红一军团第二师和师团部曾在丙安扎营，保证红军顺利一渡<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>，取得了战略性的胜利。丙安的红一军团纪念馆已成为红一军团在全国唯一的纪念馆。<br> 吊脚楼、石板路、双龙桥，这些古老的符号让人有时光倒错、神秘悠远的感觉。在吊脚楼敞开的窗前，俯瞰流淌的<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>河、耳畔嘶嘶蝉鸣、品尝美味的腊肉鲜笋和麻辣豆花，真有如世外<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63581.html">桃源</a>一般。<br> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15943.html"> 丙安古镇</a>门票20（据说晚六点以后不收门票）。古镇不大，游览时间可长可短，一两小时足矣，有卖土特产的小店，<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63538.html">比如</a>竹制品什么的，比在<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>市区买要便宜。游览完毕，从大吊桥返回公路等候回<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>的小面，坐满发车。<br> <br></p> 
