<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/32946088.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/E4/60/wKgB4lNTYbmAVxckABArxzDTLow18.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15943.html">丙安古镇</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/32946089.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/E4/7A/wKgB4lNTYdaAV4qZAA6UP__ISOA44.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15943.html">丙安古镇</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/32946090.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file26.mafengwo.net/M00/E4/19/wKgB4lNTYXmAEsOcABFM3pF9-yg76.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15943.html">丙安古镇</a></p> 
<p> &nbsp;<br> 友情提示：看攻略说“从<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/80396.html">金沙</a>去<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩</a>路近”，我们原也打算从<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15943.html">丙安古镇</a>去<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/80396.html">金沙</a>村住，但实际从丙安到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/80396.html">金沙</a>车极少非常不便，所以返回<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>住宿。其实从<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩</a>也很方便，所以建议朋友们应从<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>去各景点，否则也可包车（每天400~500）。<br> <br> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html"> 赤水</a>的住宿，我向大家推荐<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/hotel/93960.html">速8酒店</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;，<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>唯一的一家速8位于<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>河畔河滨西路168号，步行至旅游长途汽车客运站七分钟，步行到九支<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>大桥约15分钟。速8还提供免费早餐。<br> D2（2014-04-03）:<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15975.html">四洞沟</a>，<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15942.html">大同古镇</a>。住<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>。<br> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html"> 赤水</a>当地，习惯把瀑布称为“洞”，因此“<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15975.html">四洞沟</a>”就是“有四个瀑布的沟”，同样的称谓还有“<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15973.html">十丈洞</a>”，就是指<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>最大的一个瀑布。有人认为“洞”的意思是每个瀑布后面都有一个洞，其实是误解。<br> 从<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15975.html">四洞沟</a>的小面包在<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>客运站发车，坐满即走，票价10元。<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15975.html">四洞沟</a>距<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>17公里，但因路太烂，大约时程要1.5小时。景区门票30。<br> <br></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33567844.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file26.mafengwo.net/M00/A8/D5/wKgB4lNjKMSAXJvrAAlX2P-mxMk60.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a></p> 
<p> &nbsp;<br> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15975.html"> 四洞沟</a>又名闽溪，全长4.88公里。从沟口溯溪而上有四幅瀑布，依次为水帘洞、月亮谭、飞蛙崖、白龙潭。四幅瀑布形态各异。由上图可见，沿闽溪两侧修有栈道，由于栈道坡度不大，走起来并不辛苦，而且沿途风景很不错，因此建议全程徒步，由左侧入沟右侧返回，耗时大约3小时。景区内有公路及交通车，起点在沟口，终点在二、三瀑布之间，如果往返都乘交通车，就只能看三、四瀑布了。<br> 景区里竹影婆娑，古老的桫椤树随处可见，流水潺潺，空气清新，行走其间真是享受大自然的馈赠。<br></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33109796.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/B9/5A/wKgB4lNWQ2KAU_vSABOmscss4jQ14.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15975.html">四洞沟</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33109797.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/B9/82/wKgB4lNWQ3eAJcVnAA9XeBBAj6U21.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15975.html">四洞沟</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33109798.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/B9/A2/wKgB4lNWQ4uAaq3MAA-EjaXYIbc77.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15975.html">四洞沟</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33109799.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file26.mafengwo.net/M00/B9/BD/wKgB4lNWQ5yAFnFtAAxZaQHo3d439.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15975.html">四洞沟</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33109800.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file26.mafengwo.net/M00/B9/31/wKgB4lNWQ0mAZRxeABFQUq2jzc885.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15975.html">四洞沟</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33109801.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/B9/EC/wKgB4lNWQ7WAPaYSABMexzuKZFw49.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15975.html">四洞沟</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33109802.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/B9/00/wKgB4lNWQzKADO0hABWiJoTo3Qc72.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15975.html">四洞沟</a></p> 
<p> &nbsp;<br> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15975.html"> 四洞沟</a>景区与杨家岩（红石野谷）景区相距不远，但之间的交通不<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/143425.html">大方</a>便，可乘车返回<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>客运站再转乘去杨家岩的小面包车。从<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15975.html">四洞沟</a>返回<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>会路过<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15942.html">大同古镇</a>，可以上午游<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15975.html">四洞沟</a>然后到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15942.html">大同古镇</a>下车，游览古镇顺便吃午饭，饭后乘车返回<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>。<br> </p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33109803.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file26.mafengwo.net/M00/BC/07/wKgB4lNWRI6AZ5T9ABC4KLb6Ofo32.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15942.html">大同古镇</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33109804.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/BC/42/wKgB4lNWRKaAIs_EABHDytVQiV481.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15942.html">大同古镇</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33109805.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/BC/68/wKgB4lNWRLiARDLNAA3Qfod9NmA84.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15942.html">大同古镇</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33109806.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/BC/96/wKgB4lNWRMyAPt9bAA8o5rR842A92.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15942.html">大同古镇</a></p> 
<p> <br> D3（2014-04-04）：<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩</a>、五柱峰，住<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>。<br> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html"> 赤水</a>到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩</a>五柱峰景区没有专线车，要到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>旅游汽车站乘“<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>-太平渡”的长途车，买票到“大群”，上车后告诉司乘你要到“<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩</a>”，客车会在<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩</a>景区大门停车，票价15元。景区门票30。从景区大门买票，乘电瓶车（3公里，单程10元），终点到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩</a>方向和五柱峰方向的三岔路口，左侧是<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩</a>，右侧五柱峰。在<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩</a>和五柱峰之间有路相通（见下图红色路线），但走环线需要约4~5小时，如分别到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩</a>和五柱峰观景台，大约2~2.5小时。<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩</a>是溯溪而上全程石阶向上，沿途不断有些小瀑布，<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩</a>的景致非常独特，弧形直上直下的红色岩壁，一泓飞瀑直流而下，壮观又令人震撼。登五柱峰沿途没什么风景，到观景台原路返回。看完再乘交通车返回景区大门，等回<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>的车，招手即上。<br> </p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33567845.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/AA/2E/wKgB4lNjKjiAFvn2ACpbT0sn6UE55.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩景区</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33280007.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/3E/3A/wKgB4lNaVxWAGQtsAA56W8BrZB814.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩景区</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33280008.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/3F/06/wKgB4lNaV7qAETa-AAtwxsV4lNY30.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩景区</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33280009.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/42/EE/wKgB4lNaXB6AbVFFAA-U4pNWABI38.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩景区</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33280010.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/44/0A/wKgB4lNaXQiALHanADptx_ThTOI73.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15969.html">佛光岩景区</a></p> 
<p> <br> D4（2014-04-05）：<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15973.html">十丈洞</a>（<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>大瀑布）。<br> “<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15973.html">十丈洞</a>”是<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>最大的瀑布，规模堪比<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13868.html">安顺</a>的“<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10085.html">黄果树瀑布</a>”。<br> 从<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>客运站有中巴到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15973.html">十丈洞</a>，票价12元，车程一小时。从下车处到景区大门要步行约二、三十分钟。门票40。这个景区有两个瀑布，一是沟尽头的大瀑布，一是半途有一个“中洞”瀑布，其余基本没有特别的景观，所以如果无意徒步就可以在景区大门处的交通车站乘车（电瓶车往返9公里，票20元）前往，先看大瀑布，然后乘交通车返回（如果看中瀑布，上车时需说明要在中洞下车）。中洞下车下到沟底看中瀑布，看完就在路旁等交通车返回大门。全程约需2个多小时。（下面景区图只供参考，其实右侧标记的小路和景点还都在规划建设中）<br> </p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33567846.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/AA/54/wKgB4lNjKnOAQMdVABC4IHHhxQM11.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15973.html">赤水大瀑布</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33567847.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/AB/3A/wKgB4lNjK32AWGcNAA2EFm_3ZWI05.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15973.html">赤水大瀑布</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33567848.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file25.mafengwo.net/M00/AE/18/wKgB4lNjLyKAQXiaAAvkIE5gU5026.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15973.html">赤水大瀑布</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10046/scenery_3042687/33567849.html"> <img src="https://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src="https://file26.mafengwo.net/M00/AB/BD/wKgB4lNjLECAGalEAAy7my4IbUA40.groupinfo.w600.jpeg" alt="" title="四月重庆至赤水行记（四洞沟、佛光岩、十丈洞、丙安古镇、大同古镇攻略）" style="max-width:500px;"></a><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15973.html">赤水大瀑布</a></p> 
<p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html"> 赤水</a>到<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15973.html">十丈洞</a>的往返有一个需要提示的是交通问题就是班车较少。景区回<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>的车，午前11点一趟车然后就是下午1点半和4点有两趟车，如还想看<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15973.html">十丈洞</a>同一线路的“燕子岩”景区，就需计算好时间以免误事。<br> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html"> 赤水</a>的景点门票都非常便宜，景区内部管理都还不错。现在<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15973.html">十丈洞</a>正在升级改造申报五星级景点，估计申成以后，门票就要涨价了。<br> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html"> 赤水</a>有美景也有美食。这一带喜欢吃“豆花”，有“白豆花”和“黑豆花”。豆花的密度介于北方的豆腐和豆腐脑之间，可用筷子夹起蘸调料吃。春天的<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10046.html">赤水</a>盛产竹笋，鲜竹笋又脆又甜，和腊肉同炒真是“绝配”，一定不能错过哟！另外特别推荐“腊猪脚筒筒笋”，猪脚软糯，筒筒笋脆嫩，汤鲜美……<br> </p> 
